接口 ReadwriteSplittingDistSQLStatementVisitor<T>

  • 类型参数:
    T - The return type of the visit operation. Use Void for operations with no return type.
    所有超级接口:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeVisitor<T>
    所有已知实现类:
    ReadwriteSplittingDistSQLStatementBaseVisitor, ReadwriteSplittingDistSQLStatementVisitor
    public interface ReadwriteSplittingDistSQLStatementVisitor<T>
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeVisitor<T>
    This interface defines a complete generic visitor for a parse tree produced by ReadwriteSplittingDistSQLStatementParser.
